## 概念代码

```c++
class Target
{
public:
	virtual void request() {}
}

class Adaptee
{
public:
	virtual void request2() {}
};

//类适配器
class Adapter1 : public Target, public Adaptee
{
public:
	void request()
	{
		request2();
	}
}
//对象适配器
class Adapter2 : public Target
{
public:
	void request()
	{
		m_adaptee.request2();
	}
private:
	Adaptee m_adaptee
}
```
